1.title: La Locanda and Kunfusion
1.plot: La Locanda features authentic Northern Italian cuisine, old world charm and a wonderful wine list. This is the perfect restaurant for a romantic meal or an amazing lunch. La Locanda recommends making reservations by calling 8055481750. They are open Tuesday thru Sunday for lunch from 11:30 to 2:00pm and dinners from 5:00pm to 9:00pm, they are closed Monday. They are located at 1137 Garden Street in San Luis Obispo.

5.title: Penny's All American Cafe and Hush Harbor Artisan Bakery and Cafe
5.plot: Located in the heart of Atascadero, Hush Harbor Artisan Bakery and Café has become an important part of the community, bringing love, joy and sustenance to all who enter their doors. Come and meet the family, and experience the best bread and pastries on the entire coast. The bakery hours are Monday and Tuesday 7 am to 4 pm, Wednesday from 7 am to 5 pm and Saturday from 7 am to 4 pm. Lunch starts daily at 11:00 am. They are open for breakfast on Saturdays only from 7 am to 10:30 am. They are closed on Sunday. Located at 5735 El Camino Real in Atascadero, you can call ...

6.title: Mistura and Fig Good Food
6.plot: Mistura is located at 700 Clubhouse Drive in Paso Robles, on the River Oaks Golf Course. You can call for reservations and catering at (805) 238-3333. They are open for lunch Tuesday thru Saturday from 11am to 2pm, dinners Tuesday thru Thursday from. 4pm to 9pm, and Friday and Saturday from 4pm to 10pm. Sunday brunch (a deal at $35 each) is from 10am to 2pm. They are closed on Mondays.

7.title: Rooney's Irish Pub and Papi's Grill
7.plot: Rooney's Irish Pub is located at 241 S. Broadway Street in Old Town Orcutt or you can call them at (805) 934-3777. They are open Sundays- Thursday from 10:00am to 11:00pm and Friday and Saturday from 11:30am to 2:00am. At Rooney's, "There are no strangers, only friends we have never met." Come and try what all the foodies are talking about at Papi's Grill Tacos y mas. It is located at 1090 Price Street in Pismo Beach; you can reach them at 805-295-6660. They are open from 11:00am to 8:00pm daily.

8.title: The Spoon Trade and Fruitland La Casa Del Sabor
8.plot: The Spoon Trade is casual dining with a bit of panache; they also have burgers, soups and salads. They are open every night but Wednesdays from 5:00pm to 10:00pm and are located at 295 Grand Avenue in Grover Beach. You can call them at (805) 904-6773. Fruitland la Casa del Sabor is one of those rare culinary happenings where an entire family is making sure you are satisfied with their fresh, amazing food. imdb.plot outline: Taste Buds is a 30-minute visual feast featuring the finest chefs and eateries. Both big and small. Large restaurants will be featured where the Chef/Owner tells about his history, his passion's and shares some tips in his kitchen. Teri is then joined by a Taste Bud (foodie) and they taste and comment on the food. Then the Chef/Owner will venture to a "Hidden Treasure" and meet a new chef, join him in the kitchen, taste his food and become the food critic.
